Replace field stats API loop with this bulk call/aggregation

size should be the number of indices being queried.

```json
POST /csv_list_of_indices/_search?size=0
{
  "aggs": {
    "indices": {
      "terms": {
        "field": "_index",
        "size": number_of_indices_in_csv_list_of_indices
      },
      "aggs": {
        "min" : { "min" : { "field" : field } },
        "max" : { "max" : { "field" : field } }
      }
    }
  }
}
```
